This tile, when installed, enables you to use DX Application Performance Management (APM) on Pivotal Cloud Foundry (PCF).

## <a id='overview'></a>Overview

The **DX Application Performance Management for PCF** tile delivers the necessary components to monitor your applications on PCF. Once installed, the **DX Application Performance Management for PCF** service becomes available in your PCF Marketplace.

## <a id='features'></a>Key Features

DX APM for PCF currently supports the following:  

* Java (Buildpack v4.15+)
* .NET/.NET Core

