## <a id="reqs"></a>Requirements

DX APM for PCF has the following requirements:

+ A DX APM SaaS subscription or a DX APM on-premise installation

+ [Redis for PCF] (https://network.pivotal.io/products/p-redis) with Lua scripting enabled.


